N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 404.3 - Territorial application

State Regulations

The provisions of this Subchapter shall be effective
within, upon and in the airspace above all property that is presently or shall
in the future be under the jurisdiction, custody or control of the commission
within the eighth park region unless otherwise provided. Notes
